Inheritance:
this, super
default, protected and public are inherited by children 
Duck extends Bird : Syntax
Multiple inheritance not allowed. Dog cannot inherit from Animal and Mammal because same function cannot be inherited from multiple places. Hence not allowed


Interface:
Duck implements Bird 
All members public 
Can define constants nothing else 
Multiple inheritance allowed
Interfaces allow common code for both manager and programmer by allowing definition for employee

employee[] -> 1. Manager, 2. Programmer
abstract class: no instance, Employee: Manager/Programmer


Checked exceptions need not be specified in try catch method signature
custom: extends exception


